data.description: Northeast San Antonio where there is growth, business and expansion everywhere.  This 2 story home features 2 living areas, a bonus room downstairs at the entry and The Primary bedroom is Downstairs!!  The spacious upstairs offers a large open game room and 3 bedrooms.  Open floor plan with kitchen granite center island.  The owners will leave you with a move in ready home and convey many wonderful accessories such as Water softener, Refrigerator and  security camera system (Night Owl X).  AS well.....solar panels are another plus.  Who isn't looking for low utility bills in our San Antonio Heat!  Look no further!  As per seller, this home has a yearly average of under $100 per month for CPS utilities thanks to the Solar Panels.  Entry into home offers a study/office or secondary living space!    2 living areas, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms makes this home a great choice.   Please allow a 2 hour notice before viewing and appreciating this great home!
